    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The psychology faculty brings about as many curriculum courses to offer the children with more overt knowledge",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus of the good is soo good the environment, the greenery, the temple, lake everything is there!",
          "name": "sakshi narvekar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Junior college teachers and staff are very polite and friendly",
          "name": "Hrishita Dubey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They have all the sports activities and a amazing ground",
          "name": "Hrishita Dubey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "It's just 15 min walk away from Andheri Railway Station.",
          "name": "Avesh Saiyad",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The library is good and u can take book from the library n have to return it on the some day",
          "name": "Maaz Shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Big ground and lake very big with a football ground",
          "name": "KANAD RAMCHANDRA GAWADE",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "The canteen food is also good and affordable.",
          "name": "Sanjana  Raut",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Reading room for studying,where there is pin drop silence",
          "name": "Mohammed Shabbir",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Shiva temple which is situated in middle of the campus.",
          "name": "Sanjana  Raut",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The washrooms are of poor sanitation,and there's alot of water shortage",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "They dont allow us to hangout in the campus. The watchemans are too rude",
          "name": "Hrishita Dubey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The staff on the counter are way too rude with the students",
          "name": "Hrishita Dubey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "If you really need help regarding something the teachers do not reply on chats.",
          "name": "Hrishita Dubey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They need to enhance the placement system so that they can give a bright future to students. Right now, the students are struggling for jobs. Some of the students go for higher studies.",
          "name": "Maaz Shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "For me I don't like all the fest and events",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In my college cafeteria is good but personal I don't like the taste",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The dresscode rule is something I highly dislike",
          "name": "Sneha",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Attendence is compulsary for 75% there are no exception even if you are doing job",
          "name": "Akash Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "More classrooms and labs are needed for post graduation batches.",
          "name": "Shreya Shivalkar",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "Mumbai University, Mumbai"
    }
  },
